high_descs: Move to stand in front of the black shelving at the edge of the counter to the left of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the butter knife from the top of the black shelving.
Slice the bread with the knife that's too the left of the tomato.
Move to the white table against the wall left of the shelving and stand in front of the pan.
Place the knife in the pan.
Turn and move back to stand in front of the bread you just sliced.
Pick up a piece of the bread you sliced.
Carry the slice of bread to the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the slice of bread on the top shelf, close the door, wait till it's chilled, and then remove the bread.
Carry the slice of the bread back to the shelving unit where it came from.
Place the sliced bread on the top of the shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of cooled bread on the black shelving unit.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the white table, turn right, go to the black stand to the left of the counter.
Take the knife from the stand.
Cut the apple on the left into pieces on the stand.
Turn left to face the white table.
Put the knife on the blue pan on the table.
Turn right to face the black stand.
Take a piece of apple from the table.
Turn right, go straight, turn left at the fridge.
Put the apple on the top shelf of the bottom compartment of the fridge. Close and open the fridge door. Take the apple.
Turn left, go to the white table, turn right to face the black stand.
Put the apple on the stand in front of the salt.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold piece of apple on a stand.

high_descs: Turn right, head towards the toaster, and then turn right towards the square black table.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Slice the green apple into three pieces.
Turn left and face the pan on the table.
Place the knife on the pan.
Turn right to face the black table.
Pick up a slice of apple from the table.
Turn right and head towards the fridge on your left.
Open the fridge, place the apple next to the plate, close the fridge to let it cool, open the fridge to take it back out.
Turn left, head towards the long white table, and then turn right to face the black table.
Place the slice apple in front of the salt shaker on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool, sliced apple in front of the salt shaker on the black table.
